OL,3,CRetail staff face 'daily' aggressive
OL,4,Cbehaviour from shoplifters
OL,6,FRetail staff say they face daily
OL,7,F'scary, aggressive and threatening
OL,8,Fbehaviour' from shoplifters.
OL,10,FAcross Hampshire and the Isle of Wight
OL,11,Fthere has been a dramatic rise in
OL,12,Fretail thefts, with 13,024 reports
OL,13,Fover the past year - which is up by
OL,14,Fnearly 40%.
OL,16,FStaff member at River Island, Rebecca
OL,17,FMudie, said: "I've had to fight people
OL,18,Foff at the door trying not to let them
OL,19,Fin the shop but unfortunately they
OL,20,Fwill make their way in if they want to
OL,21,Fget into the shop.
