OL,3,CRetail staff face 'daily' aggressive
OL,4,Cbehaviour from shoplifters
OL,6,FRebecca Mudie works as the host at
OL,7,FRiver Island on the high street in
OL,8,FPortsmouth.
OL,10,F"It's scary for people to come into
OL,11,Fwork and have to deal with these
OL,12,Fpeople that are shoplifting from us
OL,13,Fand being aggressive.
OL,15,F"The shop suffers, the company
OL,16,Fsuffers, and personally I suffer as
OL,17,Fwell because they can be aggressive
OL,18,Ftowards me on a daily basis.
OL,20,F"It is not a victimless crime in any
OL,21,Fway shape or form."
