OL,3,CRetail staff face 'daily' aggressive
OL,4,Cbehaviour from shoplifters
OL,6,FStaff at Sainsbury's are among
OL,7,Fretailers in Portsmouth working with
OL,8,Fthe police to help stop these crimes.
OL,10,FCustomer training manager at
OL,11,FSainsbury's, Daisy Potter, said: "Our
OL,12,Fincidents range from relatively mild,
OL,13,Fcoming in swiping the shelves and
OL,14,Fleaving again, to more extreme
OL,15,Fexamples where shoplifters come in and
OL,16,Fwhen asked to leave they smash
OL,17,Fglasses, threaten staff.
OL,19,F"Our store's guard has been assaulted
OL,20,Fnumerous times by different groups of
OL,21,Fpeople."
