OL,6,FWhen asked about the impact this has
OL,7,Fon the business and customers, she
OL,8,Fsaid: "Once there's a shortage and
OL,9,Favailability issues with products,
OL,10,Fprices can go up.
OL,12,F"A lot of people rely on daily
OL,13,Freductions but when things are being
OL,14,Fcleared off the self there's not an
OL,15,Fopportunity to reduce them for the
OL,16,Fcustomers that come in specifically
OL,17,Ffor that."
