OL,3,CRetail staff face 'daily' aggressive
OL,4,Cbehaviour from shoplifters
OL,6,FHampshire Constabulary has been
OL,7,Fworking with businesses in Portsmouth
OL,8,Fcity centre to help them report
OL,9,Fshoplifting more easily.
OL,11,FOfficers say they are now using facial
OL,12,Frecognition technology, which involves
OL,13,Fbusinesses handing footage over to
OL,14,Fpolice which is run through a database
OL,15,Fto help identify the criminals.
OL,17,FIt has led to more people pleading
OL,18,Fguilty when cases go to court due to
OL,19,Fthe evidence against them.
