OL,3,CRetail staff face 'daily' aggressive
OL,4,Cbehaviour from shoplifters
OL,6,FChief Constable for Hampshire and Isle
OL,7,Fof Wight Constabulary, Scott Chilton,
OL,8,Fsaid: "I know that a lot of business
OL,9,Fowners haven't been reporting
OL,10,Fshoplifting, that's both independent
OL,11,Fshops and larger organisations.
OL,13,F"Now we've got more dedicated patrol
OL,14,Fofficers in neighbourhood teams, we've
OL,15,Fgot beat bobbies out there speaking to
OL,16,Fpeople, a different policy for
OL,17,Fdeploying to these types of crimes.
