OL,3,CRetail staff face 'daily' aggressive
OL,4,Cbehaviour from shoplifters
OL,6,F"I've also got specialist officers
OL,7,Fworking behind the scenes - targeting
OL,8,Fthose prolific offenders who are
OL,9,Ftrying to make a living out of
OL,10,Fshoplifting."
OL,12,FSentences for shoplifting can range
OL,13,Ffrom community orders and fines to
OL,14,Fjail terms of around 12 weeks.
OL,16,FThe county's Police and Crime
OL,17,FCommissioner is calling for tougher
OL,18,Fsentences and see shoplifters behind
OL,19,Fbars for longer periods.
